                "caption": "Figure 4:Overview of the proposed VLA adaptation approach.(a) We compute update-vectorsΔm,s​r​c\\mathrm{\\Delta}_{m,src}andΔm,t​g​t\\mathrm{\\Delta}_{m,tgt}by fine-tuning a base policyθ0\\theta_{0}on a single task𝒯m\\mathcal{T}_{m}using source and target data.\n(b) A domain vectorδ~t​g​t\\tilde{\\delta}_{tgt}is extracted by subtracting task directions, with subspace filtering to suppress misaligned components.\nAddingδ~t​g​t\\tilde{\\delta}_{tgt}back toθ0\\theta_{0}yields a multi-task policyθ∗\\theta^{*}adapted to the target domain.",
